params.amount: The amount to move to the fees pool.
params.payingToken: The address of the token used to pay fees.

returns._0: A boolean indicating the success of the transfer.

params.token: The address of the supported token.

returns._0: The balance of the token held by the contract.

params.inputToken: The address of the input token.
params.outputToken: The address of the output token.

params.feeRate: The fee rate, expressed as a percentage (e.g., 5 for 0.5%).
params.feesPoolAddress: The address where fees are collected.
params.tokenA: The address of the first supported token.
params.tokenB: The address of the second supported token.

params.inputAmount: The amount of input token to swap, in 18 decimals. e.g inputAmount=1e18 to swap 1 token.
params.inputToken: The address of the token we're swapping from.
params.outputToken: The address of the output token we're swapping to.

returns._0: A boolean indicating the success of the swap.
